    <item>
      <title>关税风波中黄金交易商以大幅折扣抛售英国央行黄金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gold-dealers-sell-boe-bullion-at-big-discounts-in-tariff-panic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对特朗普潜在关税的担忧引发了对金条的争夺，导致人们排队数周才能提取黄金，英格兰银行金库中的黄金交易价格低于大盘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gold-dealers-sell-boe-bullion-at-big-discounts-in-tariff-panic</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 18:16:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Jim Chanos 称 DeepSeek 凸显了支付高额 AI 倍数的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/chanos-deepseek-underscores-risks-of-high-ai-multiples-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Chanos &amp; Company 总裁兼创始人 Jim Chanos 结合 DeepSeek 对 AI 领域公司的影响，探讨了颠覆性技术的市场风险。他在“彭博市场”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/chanos-deepseek-underscores-risks-of-high-ai-multiples-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 18:11:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Janus 推出首只选股 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/janus-launches-its-first-stock-picking-etf-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Janus Henderson 也倾向于选股策略。今天，该公司推出了一只新的主动管理型股票 ETF，其投资组合包括约 20 至 30 只股票。它被称为转型增长股票 ETF。Janus Henderson 美洲股票主管 Marc Pinto 参加了彭博公开交易，谈论新产品。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/janus-launches-its-first-stock-picking-etf-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 18:10:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>查诺斯称对中国征收 10% 关税“行不通”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/10-tariff-against-china-won-t-do-it-chanos-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Chanos &amp; Company 总裁兼创始人 Jim Chanos 表示，美国对中国征收 10% 的关税不会带来太大影响。他说，这些关税将损害本已疲软的经济。他接受了彭博社 Scarlet Fu 和 Romaine Bostick 的独家采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/10-tariff-against-china-won-t-do-it-chanos-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 17:51:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东原油价格飙升 沙特阿美提高对亚洲的石油价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/saudi-aramco-boosts-oil-prices-to-asia-as-mideast-crude-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为应对中东原油溢价飙升及炼油厂利润率提高，沙特阿拉伯将其对亚洲的旗舰原油价格上调了两年多来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/saudi-aramco-boosts-oil-prices-to-asia-as-mideast-crude-soars</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 17:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金价格因避险需求创下新高，但供应紧俏局面持续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-trade-war-stokes-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于贸易战忧虑增强了避险需求且市场短期紧缩迹象持续存在，金价从历史新高回吐涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-trade-war-stokes-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 00:08:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普上台后，交易员纷纷逃离市场，油价或维持在 2025 年低点附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统就职后的几周内，交易员继续退出市场，油价维持在 2025 年的最低水平附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 23:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券价格上涨，股票交易员不再担心人工智能：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于大多数主要行业的增长盖过了部分科技巨头业绩不佳的影响，股市出现反弹。美国服务业数据疲软，债券价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 22:44:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利因需求激增而出售 55 亿美元 X 债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/morgan-stanley-boosts-x-debt-sale-as-investors-embrace-musk-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于投资者需求强于预期，由摩根士丹利牵头的多家银行正在出售与伊隆马斯克的社交媒体平台 X 相关的 55 亿美元债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/morgan-stanley-boosts-x-debt-sale-as-investors-embrace-musk-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 18:51:45 GMT</pubDate>
